title: The Mars Volta, Live at the Troubadour, LA, 2007 (SBD-remaster)
description:
This is my own remaster of The Mars Voltas Troubadour-concert in LA, 2007-04-02, showing an amazingly powerful band, playing all of the heavier tracks from Amputechture. 

Tracklist:

1. Goliath
2. Haunt of Roulette Dares
3. Cygnus... Vismund Cygnus
4. Viscera Eyes
5. Wax Simulacra
6. Drunkships of Lanterns
7. Vermicide
8. Tetragrammaton
9. Meccamputechture
10. Day of the Baphomets

Setlength: 114 minutes.


The original source was probably stereo-out from the soundboard. The work done on the sound is mainly EQ-ing and limiting, the sound quality going from decent to pretty good.
